That's my y-axis.

00:00:22.360 --> 00:00:27.520
And here is my x-axis.

00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:31.250
And then the parabola y
squared is equal to 4x

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:32.450
would look like this.

00:00:32.450 --> 00:00:33.755
Something like that.

00:00:33.755 --> 00:00:35.869
That would be in
the first quadrant,

00:00:35.869 --> 00:00:37.660
and then it would be
symmetric around that.

00:00:37.660 --> 00:00:39.010
It would look like that.

00:00:39.010 --> 00:00:43.160
So this would be y
squared is equal to 4x.

00:00:43.160 --> 00:00:46.080
Or if I just focused on
this top part over here,

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:48.300
